# Test substrings
set sentence Hello World
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 0 5    |assert equals string Hello}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 6 11   |assert equals string World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 0 11   |assert equals string Hello World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 0 100  |assert equals string Hello World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 6 100  |assert equals string World}
eval nop {global:sentence|substring 100 200|assert equals string}

exit